 other hepatotoxic agents, and vice versa.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/4463/', '', 'Salicylic acid, Salsalate, Choline salicylate, Diflunisal, Methoxyflurane, Acetylsalicylic acid, Acetylsalicylic acid, Naloxone', 'Brivaracetam, Rufinamide, Methsuximide, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Paramethadione, Perampanel, Fenfluramine, Eslicarbazepine, Ganaxolone, Phensuximide, More', 1767369485);
